{
  "number": 26,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/26",
  "title": "[hierarchicalMenu] create widget",
  "body": "This widget needs to be able to render this:\n\n![2015-08-05-103406_416x463_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/9081556/8520218c-3b5d-11e5-9474-c66d1f527310.png)\n## API\n\nReuse the menu widget and add `hierarchicalFacetNames` to be given:\n\n``` js\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.hierarchicalMenu({\n    container: '#categories', \n    attributes: ['categories.lvl0', 'categories.lvl1']\n  })\n);\n```\n\nIf both facetName and hierarchicalFacetNames are given, throw.\n",
